## Summary
This documentation page provides an overview of Amplitude Activation, a self-service personalization platform that enables true one-to-one personalization without requiring data science or engineering resources. It explains how the platform helps marketers identify optimal user segments through cohorts and computations, allows product teams to determine personalized next actions through predictions and recommendations, and enables engineers to export data to digital channels for real-time personalization.

